e":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"quote":{"pid":"d9da5f73a2dca8968eed90787baddc1e9352f744","tid":2492482,"uid":37524,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T07:07:50.000Z","msg":"香港出名多閪客<br />\n譚仔姐姐應該唔容易做噃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T07:20:32.000Z","msg":"譚仔請呀姐就係因為啲姐姐唔怕閪客，勇敢像個袓國人咁唔俾人恰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試過見過有條友嘈啲姐姐嗌凍奶茶變左凍0茶，正常出面換過杯就算，係個譚仔姐姐用大聲口音力拗自己無錯到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個份氣勢令周圍既人都覺得係閪客亂吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然最後緊係姐姐聽錯啦<br />\n口噏噏換過杯俾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb7989c959fbc313c2ca103c287528c1a90b34d","tid":2492482,"uid":258174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f39a5b6f4ea12c35d3666897e0df80fccbed2c87","tid":2492482,"uid":366470,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T07:09:02.000Z","msg":"做幾多個鐘先?<br />\n好似我做part time嗰間茶記咁<br />\n有個樓面時薪65蚊<br />\n但係一日只係返4個鐘<br />\n6天工作週<br />\n所以月薪只係得7千零蚊左右"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T07:25:14.000Z","msg":"人地講緊全職喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df1a063648dd1669417ddcafd19f8e8bd21b88f","tid":2492482,"uid":366470,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"bbb7989c959fbc313c2ca103c287528c1a90b34d","tid":2492482,"uid":258174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f39a5b6f4ea12c35d3666897e0df80fccbed2c87","tid":2492482,"uid":366470,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T07:09:02.000Z","msg":"做幾多個鐘先?<br />\n好似我做part time嗰間茶記咁<br />\n有個樓面時薪65蚊<br />\n但係一日只係返4個鐘<br />\n6天工作週<br />\n所以月薪只係得7千零蚊左右"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T07:25:14.000Z","msg":"人地講緊全職喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}